Circuit Connections
_____________________


MAX30105:
__________

VCC → 3.3V

GND → GND

SDA → GPIO 21

SCL → GPIO 22


  MPU6050:
  __________

VCC → 3.3V

GND → GND

SDA → GPIO 21

SCL → GPIO 22


  DHT11:
  __________

VCC → 3.3V

GND → GND

Data → GPIO 15


   LEDs:
  ________

Pulse LED → GPIO 2

Read LED → GPIO 4


  Power:
  _______

ESP32 powered via USB or external 5V supply.
